# Contributing to Kimitsu

Thanks for your interest in contributing. Kimitsu is early-stage and the architecture is still evolving — please read this before opening a PR.

---

## Project Status

Kimitsu is pre-1.0. Core abstractions are stable but implementation details change frequently. Large contributions that look good in isolation may conflict with roadmap direction. **Open an issue before writing significant code.** This protects your time as much as ours.

---

## Getting Started

**Requirements**
- Go 1.22+
- Docker (for running the full stack)

**Build**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/kimitsu-ai/ktsu.git
cd ktsu
go build ./...
```

**Run tests**
```bash
go test ./...
```

**Run the full stack locally**
```bash
ktsu new project my-test
cd my-test
ktsu start --all --env environments/dev.env.yaml
```

**Validate a project**
```bash
ktsu validate
```

